{{Infobox football biography |name = Aaron Rowe |image = |image_size = |caption = |fullname = Aaron Rowe |birth_date = {{birth date and age|2000|9|7|df=y}} |birth_place = [[London]] |height = |position = [[Midfielder#Winger|Winger]] |currentclub = [[Huddersfield Town A.F.C.|Huddersfield Town]] |clubnumber = 44 |youthyears1 = ?–2018 |youthclubs1 = [[Leyton Orient F.C.|Leyton Orient]] |youthyears2 = 2018–2019 |youthclubs2 = [[Huddersfield Town A.F.C.|Huddersfield Town]] |years1 = 2019– |clubs1 = [[Huddersfield Town A.F.C.|Huddersfield Town]] |caps1 = 2 |goals1 = 0 |club-update = 17:08, 16th March 2019 (UTC) }} '''Aaron Rowe''' (born 7 September 2000) is an English professional [[association football|footballer]] who plays for [[Huddersfield Town A.F.C.|Huddersfield Town]], as a [[Midfielder#Winger|winger]].
==Club career== Rowe joined [[Leyton Orient F.C.|Leyton Orient]] and made a number of appearances for their under 18 side during the 2016 to 2018 period.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.leytonorient.com/news/2016/october/u18-report-cambridge-united-0-2-leyton-orient/|title=U18 REPORT: Cambridge United 0-2 Leyton Orient|publisher=Leyton Orient F.C.}}</ref>
He signed for [[Huddersfield Town A.F.C.|Huddersfield Town]] in February 2018.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.htafc.com/teams/u19-team/midfielder/aaron-rowe/|title=Aaron Rowe |publisher=Huddersfield Town F.C.}}</ref> Rowe made his senior debut on 9 March 2019, in a 2–0 home [[Premier League]] defeat against [[A.F.C. Bournemouth|AFC Bournemouth]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.examinerlive.co.uk/sport/football/news/who-aaron-rowe-huddersfield-town-15948133|title=Who is Huddersfield Town Premier League call-up Aaron Rowe?|first=Mel|last=Booth|date=9 March 2019|work=Huddersfield Examiner}}</ref>
==Personal life== Rowe is the younger brother of former [[Southampton F.C.|Southampton]] man [[Omar Rowe]], who currently plays in Cyprus.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://englishplayersabroad.com/2018/08/07/omar-rowe-the-former-saints-winger-whos-worked-his-way-up-the-divisions-in-cyprus/|title=Omar Rowe: The former Saints winger who’s worked his way up the divisions in Cyprus|website=englishplayersabroad.com|date=7 August 2018|accessdate=20 March 2019}}</ref>
